# TypeScript / JavaScript

- Prefer functional components and hooks in React
- Use functional `setState` updates when state depends on previous value
- Import directly from source files — avoid barrel imports for large libraries
- Use `toSorted()` instead of `.sort()` on props/state arrays
- Dynamic import heavy components not needed on first paint
